msgid ""
"Article on which customers will land by default. The search is limited to "
"this article, unless it is the workspace root, in which case all child "
"articles are included."
msgstr ""
"Artikel waar klanten standaard terechtkomen. De zoekopdracht is beperkt tot "
"dit artikel, tenzij het de root van de werkruimte is, in welk geval alle "
"onderliggende artikelen worden meegenomen."

